args: We're back, and we've got a\nmeow-tric ton of stuff with us!
The two of us are making great progress!
*purr* It feels so nice when\nyou pet me like that...
Seems like you two are getting along just\nswimmingly. Perhaps it is on account of\nyour matching gear sets.
It doesn't hurt, that's for sure.\nWhen we hit the trail in these duds,\nit makes me shivery all over!
Wonderful. And given your impressive\nteamwork, I've a request for you both.
I've heard tell of a strange fiend roaming\nthese parts lately, and I'd like you to find\nout the story.
That does sound like it's worth\ninvestigating. It could be something\nreally fur-ocious!
No worries, specs! Me and kitty here\nwill have this sorted in a jiff!
I await your news with bated breath.
So according to the researcher's nyotes,\nthe area around here is suspect.
Yeah, it's giving me the heebie-jeebies\nfor sure. Still, I'm not afraid of some\ndumb fiend! Come on out, you!
Nya! I'd say you successfully purr-voked it!
Keep your blade sharp and let's do this!
Oh wow, this thing is tough.
If it's this tough even for me...\nKitty! Hey! Watch out!
Vanessa! You got hurt purr-tecting me!
Talk later... Right now...I have to be...\nyour shield! Hraaaaagh!
No! I can't ask you to get hurt\nfor my sake. I'll be fine!
After all, what kind of Palico would I be\nif I let you do everything!
I'm not that great at working in tandem,\nbut okay! Let's try!
I'll take care of the tail while\nyou handle the horns!
Go after the horns alone?\nI've never taken on such\nan impurr-tant role...
(I'm scared... But I can do it, nya!)
All right, I cut off its tail!\nHow's it looking for you, kitty?\nUh, what the...?
Crap! I need to take out this\nstupid monster right now!
Well, we made it back in one piece.\nNot sure how that happened, but hey!
Look, I'm sorry about today. It's my fault.\nI didn't think about what I was asking you\nto do, and you ended up being hurt.
No. It was me who messed up.\nI'm the one who was weak.
You entrusted me with a key role,\nand I made a purr-fect mess of it.
And on top of that, you got hurt trying to\npurr-tect me, nya!
I'm a failure as a fur-iend.
No, it's my fault! I just didn't know your\nstrengths, is all!
Purr-lease. I just...want to be alone.
Geez, I really thought we were starting\nto understand each other, but now...
Is it all happening again?\nJust like last time?
Am I going to lose someone\nimportant to me AGAIN?
